<div><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">附件：商户（甲方）应提交的《扣款授权书》</span></p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span
                style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; widows:0"><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">扣款授权书</span></p>
    <br>
    <p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span
                style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p>
    <p style="background-color:#ffffff; font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt">
        <span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">1</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="color:#111111; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">本扣款</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">授权书（简称“授权书”）为持卡人授权</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">      </span><span
                style="color:#ff0000; font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline"><?php echo $data['fcs_lender']; ?></span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">    </span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">公司（简称“被授权人”）通过其指定的具有资质的第三方支付机构，从持卡人的还款账户中划扣应还款项所订立的有效法律文件。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-color:#ffffff; font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt">
        <span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">2</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">持卡人同意被授权人可将委托事项转委托给（</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">1</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">）被授权人的关联方；及</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">/</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">或（</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">2</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">）为向持卡人提供服务之目的而与被授权人及其关联方开展业务合作的合作方（前述主体以下统称为</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">“</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">服务方</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">”</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">）。</span></p>
    <p style="background-color:#ffffff; font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt">
        <span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5pt">3</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">持卡人勾选同意本授权书或在本授权书签字，视为持卡人不可撤销地同意并确认本授权书的所有内容，接受与本授权书有关的各项规则。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-color:#ffffff; font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt">
        <span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">4</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">持卡人同意并授权被授权人及</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">/</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">或服务方在持卡人与被授权人之间的相关基础交易或借贷协议约定的期限内，委托银行或第三方支付机构从持卡人指定的还款银行账户内划扣应还款项。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt"><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">5</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">持卡人的授权范围为持卡人与被授权人及</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">/</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">或服务方签订的一份或多份协议，具体扣款金额以协议约定为准；被授权人及第三方支付机构无须在任何一次划扣前，提前取得持卡人的同意或通知持卡人。扣款所产生的后果由持卡人本人承担，与第三方支付公司和被授权人无关。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-color:#ffffff; font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt">
        <span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">6</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">持卡人保证在还款日当日，在还款的银行账户中留有足够余额，否则因还款银行账户余额不足或不可归责于被授权人及</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">/</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">或第三方支付机构的任何事由，导致无法及时扣款或扣款错误、失败的，所有不利后果及责任由持卡人承担。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-color:#ffffff; font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt">
        <span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">7</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">持卡人拟变更还款银行账户等重要信息的，应在当期款项还款日之前</span><span
                style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">30</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">个工作日向被授权人及第三方支付机构提出变更请求。</span></p>
    <p style="background-color:#ffffff; font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 22.35pt; text-indent:-22.35pt">
        <span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:10.5pt">8</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span
                style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">持卡人保证本授权书的真实性、合法性和有效性，被授权人依据本授权书进行的委托划扣款操作引起的一切法律纠纷或风险，由持卡人独立承担或解决。</span>
    </p>
